        by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jeff-kao">Jeff Kao</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Priyanjana Bengani</span>, <a href="https://towcenter.columbia.edu/">Tow Center for Digital Journalism</a>    </span>
    <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
        <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-12-20EST06:00">Dec. 20, 6 a.m. EST</time>
    </time>

